      "date": "2014-05-28 08:34:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(23 comments)\n\nLooks like your substitution script was broken or something, since it removed all of the lnb indices from the users of this struct.\n\nThat would be fine if you are changing the code to increment \"lnb\" as it is used, though care must be taken that it isn't used elsewhere in that function or passed to a subroutine.",
